snippet.title: Overwatch 2 | Control Trailer
snippet.description:
Every journey starts somewhere.

Join Juno on her voyage to Future Earth in the newest Hero Trailer, ‘Control.’

And play as our newest Martian Support Hero TODAY in Season 12: New Frontiers.

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC!
